  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An orthosis in the ballet shoe to see if pain reduction during dancing on pointes will
      decrease.

      One group of pre-preprofessional ballet dancers will receive an orthosis and will train
      during four weeks with it. The other group without a orthosis will be the control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
